import React from 'react';

const Form = ( props ) =>(
    <form onSubmit={props.getBook}>
     <select name="list" id="selectList" label="choose a list">
        <option value="mass-market-paperback">Mass Market Paperback</option>
        <option value="combined-print-and-e-book-fiction">Combined Print and E-Book Fiction</option>
     </select>

        <input 
            type="text"
            name="bookDate"
            placeholder="YYYY-MM-DD"
            className = 'pa1'/>
        
        <label for="=lists">Choose a bestsellers list: </label>

     <button className = 'ma2 pa1'>search</button>

    </form>
);

export default Form;
